@jerrypeng I've addressed your comments.
Note that this is pr primarily focuses on the functions front-end and already does some of the optimizations that you mentioned. For instance if there is no change in the function code, we no longer upload a new copy to bk(We do a download however from existing bk location just to make sure that all the parameters are ok, this cannot be avoided). 
Making restart a first class citizen in the runtime is a follow up change
